summary: I am an enthusiastic and driven marketing, communications & PR professional, with relevant international experience within different industries. My focus lays on creating authentic and powerful brand stories that will engage and inspire the audience, enhancing their journey through both digital and off-line channels. I enjoy collaborating with people of diverse cultural and professional backgrounds, while never refusing a good challenge, neither a good laugh.
